sentences: The Secretariat introduced the item on budget performance for 2006-2007 (FCCC/SBI/2007/INF.1 and INF.5).
Chair Asadi said he will consult informally and prepare draft conclusions.
Parties considered the proposed programme budget for the biennium 2008-2009 ( FCCC/SBI/2007/8 and Adds.1-2; FCCC/SBI/2007/MISC.1 ).
Harald Dovland (Norway) will chair a contact group.
Regarding the sub-item on the implementation of paragraph 7(c) of the financial procedures of the Convention ( FCCC/SBI/2007/4 ), Chair Asadi said he will consult informally.
Regarding the UN headquarters agreement, host country GERMANY discussed the new UN campus in Bonn.
Chair Asadi will prepare draft conclusions.
enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
